He wrote: Necessity is laid upon me.
Really, woe to me if I do not declare the good news! As we imitate him, our conscience speaks to us, assuring us that we are doing the right thing.
And by preaching the good news, we appeal to the conscience of those to whom we speak.
Yes, the conscience can be an invaluable tool.
